SPECIAL DOXOLOGIES

Speoial doxologies are provided in the Breviary for oer- tain feasts and seasons. They are all written in iambio dimeters‚ and they replaee the ordinary doxologies in all hymns of the same meter.

The following doxology is said from Christmas till the Epiphany, during the Octavo of Corpus Christi, on the feasts of the Sacred Heart and Holy N ame, and on feasts of the Blessed Virgin and during their Octaves.
